{"title_page": "2009 flu pandemic table May 2009", "text_new": "{{Further|2009 swine flu pandemic by country}}\n{{See also|2009 swine flu pandemic timeline}}\n{{Main|2009 swine flu pandemic}}\n\nThis is a table containing the figures from the [[World Health Organization|WHO]] Influenza A Situation Updates issued in May 2009 roughly once a day.<ref>[http://www.who.int/csr/disease/swineflu/updates/en/index.html WHO Situation Updates]</ref>  Where more than one update was issued in a day, the corresponding figures are from the last update that day.  The table can by sorted by country, date of first confirmed case or date of first confirmed case by continent.\n\nThis presentation of the data in this and other tables shows the progression, peaks, and, eventually, decline of the epidemic in each country and continent.\n\n[[2009 flu pandemic table April 2009|Previous month]] | [[2009 flu pandemic table June 2009|Next month]]\n\n==Chart==\n{|align=\"center\"\n|- align=\"center\"\n| <u> WHO figures chart of progression </u> <ref>[http://www.who.int/csr/disease/swineflu/updates/en/index.html WHO: Situation updates - Influenza A(H1N1)]</ref>\n|-\n|\n<timeline>\nImageSize  = width:750 height:730\nPlotArea   = width:680 height:720 left:70 bottom:0\nAlignBars  = late\n\nPeriod = from:0 till:16384\nTimeAxis   = orientation:horizontal\n\nBarData=\n  bar:01/05 text:\"01/05/09\"\n  bar:02/05 text:\"02/05/09\"\n  bar:03/05 text:\"03/05/09\" link:https://web.archive.org/web/20090725004022/http://whoterrance.vo.msecnd.net/mediacentre/swine_flu/GlobalSubnationalMaster_20090503_1630_lrg.jpg\n  bar:04/05 text:\"04/05/09\" link:http://www.who.int/csr/don/H1N1map20090504.jpg\n  bar:05/05 text:\"05/05/09\" link:https://web.archive.org/web/20090716174040/http://whoterrance.vo.msecnd.net/mediacentre/swine_flu/GlobalSubnationalMaster_20090505_1610.jpg\n  bar:06/05 text:\"06/05/09\" link:http://www.who.int/csr/don/h1b120090506%5F730PM.jpg\n  bar:07/05 text:\"07/05/09\" link:http://www.who.int/csr